from far enough away,

00:54.054 --> 00:57.423
you can see a pattern.

00:57.424 --> 01:02.061
In the universe, in
nature, in life...

01:02.062 --> 01:06.065
especially even in death.

01:06.066 --> 01:09.601
The trouble is, when
you're inside the pattern,

01:09.602 --> 01:14.206
you just can't see it.

01:14.207 --> 01:18.078
